title: Piet Mondrian Lozenge Tote
description:
Tote developed from Piet Mondrian’s Lozenge Composition with Yellow, Black, Blue, Red, and Gray, 1921, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

The straightforward lines and striking primary palette of our modernist cotton canvas tote make it the perfect accessory.  

  • Dimensions: 15 x 14 in. with 11 in. shoulder strap
  • Material: 100% Cotton.
